":"雖然個post有D野係為鬧而鬧<br />\n但係無論泛民定本土，有問題唔對路就要鬧，正如813示威者做得唔好我地自己都鬧。唔鬧只會錯落去。"},{"pid":"e4b27b8019e524d7131eba858babaabde3667646","tid":1489182,"uid":50457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T22:54:57.000Z","msg":"已估到係邊個開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日日開垃圾post"},{"pid":"fb543db744e59b1a784d93f04d8215ca4c142cc2","tid":1489182,"uid":221044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T23:13:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不分化，不割蓆</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家都錯過，最緊要過程中不斷自省，改善自己同手法。泛民為我地做左咁多，我撐泛民。"},{"pid":"c593002d67411e9cebb0a0c84b53f3103abe7dfc","tid":1489182,"uid":27375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T23:23:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"ee0131de280df88e693e6fba0881fd7a9c79659a","tid":1489182,"uid":2613,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c3e631e0bee085da33ad010f3b82f2a26ce03d79","tid":1489182,"uid":1247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T22:29:57.000Z","msg":"有啲唔算拉住我地羅友既<br />\n到底佢地同我地真係同一條船丫 定係倒緊啲水入我地架船到呢<br />\n樓主到底係分化緊丫 定想點<br />\n我睇唔透<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T23:28:53.000Z","msg":"佢應該係熱狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76528c43e0d9adc8e63dfbae291bf5772e4f2a52","tid":1489182,"uid":282910,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T23:35:56.000Z","msg":"講事實又屈人熱狗"},{"pid":"91f9e2fc5e6643d531a9ef2aae0ff1b6c8338929","tid":1489182,"uid":271778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:44:25.000Z","msg":"用字中立但係選擇性報道算咩中立，你真係寫哂所有泛民做過嘅好事同壞事出黎都仲話會認真睇下"}]}